Classic Baked Potatoes

60 min
$8
250 kcal
Difficulty: 15%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

EasyComfort FoodSide Dish

Description

Fluffy, tender baked potatoes with a crispy skin, perfect for any meal!

Ingredients

  • russet potatoes: 4 large
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • butter: 4 tablespoons
  • sour cream: 1 cup
  • chives: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • shredded cheese: 1 cup
